{
  "stem": "13471.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'd buy 'em Cokes and buy 'em coffee and stuff, and I got on the inside track, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, well, there's a program, they're going to send-- they have too many shore-going officers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they're going to give some-- some special seagoing training, and would you interested?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, yes!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was, get the hell out of here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so they put it in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the boys followed it through for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They'd call me up on the phone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They'd say hey, it's going through, it's all right, it's going through.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So then all of a sudden, I get this word that it is not going through and I'm going to stay right where I am.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, I-- what the hell's going on?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I went over there and I found out what had happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My commanding officer, about three levels up, was a Navy captain who was a son of a bitch.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had seen-- by the way, this, this Wilkinson, this admiral I used to report to every morning, had given--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
